Package semanticMarkup.ling.chunk.lib.chunker

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AndChunker
    AndChunker chunks by handling "and" terminals
    AreaChunker
    AreaChunker chunks by handling an area describing terminals
    CharacterListChunker
    CharacterListChunker chunks by handling a number of character describing terminals.
    CharacterNameChunker
    AndChunker chunks by handling character name describing terminals
    ChromosomeChunker
    ChromosomeChunker chunks by handling chromosome describing terminals
    CleanupChunker
    CleanupChunker reformats the chunks after all other chunkers have been run to obtain an overall consistent chunking result
    ConjunctedOrgansRecoverChunker
    ConjunctedOrgansRecoverChunker attempts to include broken-away conjuncted organs to pp and vb phrase
    DummyChunker
    DummyChunker does not chunk.
    MyCleanupChunker
    MyCleanupChunker reformats the chunks after all other chunkers have been run to obtain an overall consistent chunking result Specifically modifier, character, constraint and organ chunks are reconsidered
    MyModifierChunker
    MyModifierChunker chunks by handling modifier terminals
    MyNewCleanupChunker
    MyCleanupChunker reformats the chunks after all other chunkers have been run to obtain an overall consistent chunking result Specifically modifier, character, constraint and organ chunks are reconsidered
    MyStateChunker
    MyStateChunker chunks by handling state terminals
    NPListChunker
    NPListChunker chunks by handling noun terminals
    NumericalChunker
    NumericalChunker chunks by handling numerical terminals
    OrChunker
    NumericalChunker chunks by handling 'or' terminals
    OrganChunker
    OrganChunker chunks by handling 'organ' terminals
    OrganRecoverChunker
    OrganRecoverChunker attempts to mark modified non-subject organs as a chunk
    OtherINsChunker
    OtherINsChunker chunks IN tags of the parse tree not handled by another chunker
    PPINChunker
    PPINChunker chunks PP followed by IN tags of the parse tree
    PPListChunker
    PPListChunker chunks conjuncted preposition phrases
    PunctuationChunker
    PunctuationChunker chunks by handling punctuation terminals
    SpecificPPChunker
    Specific PP Chunker chunks preposition phrases preceeded by a state
    StateChunker
    StateChunker chunks by handling state terminals
    ThanChunker
    ThanChunker chunks comparison phrases connected by "than", "more", etc.
    ThatChunker
    ThatChunker chunks by handling "that" terminals
    ToChunker
    ToChunker chunks by handling "to" terminals
    UnitsChunker
    UnitsChunker chunks by handling "unit" terminals
    VBChunker
    VBChunker chunks by handling verb phrases
    VPRecoverChunker
    VPRecoverChunker chunks by handling verbs not parsed as such by the parser
    WhenChunker
    WhenChunker chunks by handling 'when' terminals
    WhereChunker
    WhenChunker chunks by handling 'where' terminals
